---------

4.List of networks
  command : docker network ls

  it shows list of networks in the docker 

5.Create a one network 
  command : docker network create web-service

  it can create a network,and check the network create or not
   "docker network ls"

 example :create a two continers in one network
   1.docker run -d --name c1 -p 8080:80 --network web-service nginx    

